  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "Season the pork chops with salt, black pepper, and red chili powder.",
    "Grill the pork chops for 5-6 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the mustard paste, ginger paste, garam masala, cumin powder, coriander powder, and salt.",
    "Brush the mustard-ginger mixture on the grilled pork chops.",
    "Warm the ssam wraps by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the wraps by placing a grilled pork chop on each wrap, followed by a dollop of green chutney, cucumber slices, and a sprinkle of cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Let the pork chops rest for 5 minutes before serving to ensure juiciness.",
    "Slice the pork chops against the grain before serving.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro, if desired."
  ],
